### NetSentinel API Test Requests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Get All Devices
GET http://localhost:3001/api/devices

### Get Devices by Status
GET http://localhost:3001/api/devices?status=ONLINE

### Get Devices by Type
GET http://localhost:3001/api/devices?type=SERVER

### Get Device by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/devices/{{deviceId}}

### Create Device
POST http://localhost:3001/api/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Server",
  "ip": "192.168.1.99",
  "type": "SERVER",
  "status": "ONLINE",
  "cpuUsage": 45.5,
  "memoryUsage": 62.3,
  "temperature": 42.5,
  "uptime": 86400,
  "location": "Data Center A",
  "snmpConfig": {
    "version": "v2c",
    "community": "public",
    "port": 161,
    "timeout": 5000
  }
}

### Update Device
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/devices/{{deviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "WARNING",
  "cpuUsage": 85.5
}

### Delete Device
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/devices/{{deviceId}}

### Get All Alerts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/alerts

### Get Unacknowledged Alerts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/alerts?acknowledged=false

### Get Critical Alerts
GET http://localhost:3001/api/alerts?severity=critical

### Get Alert by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/alerts/{{alertId}}

### Create Alert
POST http://localhost:3001/api/alerts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}",
  "deviceName": "Test Server",
  "message": "High CPU usage detected",
  "severity": "warning"
}

### Acknowledge Alert
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/alerts/{{alertId}}/acknowledge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "acknowledgedBy": "admin"
}

### Delete Alert
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/alerts/{{alertId}}

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users

### Get Users by Role
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users?role=admin

### Get User by Username
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/admin

### Create User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "role": "viewer"
}

### Update User
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/users/testuser
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/users/testuser

### Get System Stats
GET http://localhost:3001/api/stats

